Your favorite Barbie Princesses have made a plan to go on an exciting adventurous trip together. They are full of happiness and excited to have the best time near the beach during the vacation of this summer. But, they all look confused what to put on and what essentials they need to carry to make their beach vacation memorable. Do you give your helping hands to these cute dolls? Join Barbie Princesses Dress Up game and get ready to guide them to pick up the cool outfits along with other important things!
They are very hopeful and rely on your excellent fashion abilities. Use your unique style sense and fashion skills to choose the best outfits for the princesses in this brand new dressing game for girls! You would see different six product categories on the left side of the screen. Firstly, click the character you want to dress up and then click the product category to explore all the available options. Give your chosen a nice hairstyle first and then come to help her select the cool outfits along with the matching accessories!
Dress her up with a nice frock and combine it with a pair of cool long socks and sandals! Give her a fabulous guitar or a laptop in her hand! The next princess will love to carry a frock with a red and blue color frock and a cute little dog in her left hand. Dress up the third and little cute princes with a yellow and purple color frock with some flowers on its top! Give her a swimming tube or a softy in her hand to complete her look in this html5 princess dress up game! Do the same for the fourth girl!
